title: Independent candidate Amjad Ali Khan wins NA-02 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Amjad Ali Khan has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-02 Swat-I by securing 88,938 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) Amir Muqam, who bagged 37,764 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 36.54 percent.
